101. Identify, how a cookie’s value can be retrieved in a web application?
<?php
// Step 1: Set a cookie (valid for 1 hour)
setcookie("user", "Keerthana", time() + 3600, "/");

// Step 2: Retrieve cookie value after page reload
if (isset($_COOKIE["user"])) {
    echo "✅ Cookie Value: " . $_COOKIE["user"];
} else {
    echo "🍪 Cookie not set yet. Please refresh the page.";
}
?>
